results.title: Avengers: The Initiative (2007) #1
results.description: After Armory's weapon causes the death of M.V.P., she washes out of the Initiative Program. The circumstances of the event have since been made hush-hush. As far as the Initiative is concerned, M.V.P. never died in Stamford...

results.title: Avengers: The Initiative (2007) #5
results.description: World War Hulk Tie-In! The Initiative program denies all knowledge of a special Black Ops Team. The Superhuman Armed Forces wishes to dispel all rumors of a 199th mutant. We repeat, there is no Mutant Zero. Mutant Zero does NOT exist. That is all.

results.title: Avengers: The Initiative (2007) #6
results.description: The Gauntlet, the Initiative's top drill instructor, has been beaten and left for dead. And all the evidence points towards his attacker being someone on the base. Who did it? A spy? A recruit? An instructor?
